meanings.definition: Not expired or out of date.
meanings.sent1: The milk in the fridge is unexpired.
meanings.sent2: Make sure to check the unexpired date on the medicine.
meanings.sent3: I found an unexpired coupon for a free coffee.
meanings.sent4: Her unexpired enthusiasm for learning is contagious.
meanings.sent5: The unexpired warranty gives me peace of mind.
